sequenceDiagram
    participant P1 as Producer 实例 A
    participant B as Broker
    participant DB as 业务数据库
    participant P2 as Producer 实例 B
    participant C as Consumer

    P1->>B: 发送 Half Message
    B-->>P1: ACK

    P1->>DB: 创建订单并提交
    DB-->>P1: COMMITTED

    P1-xB: Commit 请求丢失
    Note over B: Half Message 仍处于待决状态

    B->>P2: 回查事务状态
    P2->>DB: 按 event_id 查询
    DB-->>P2: COMMITTED
    P2-->>B: COMMIT

    B->>C: 投递最终消息
